    "body" : "<p>Spring relay on java ThreadLocal mechanism, see this: <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/lang/ThreadLocal.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/lang/ThreadLocal.html</a></p>\n\n<p>Note that if you use ThreadLocal in your code you have to manage data erasure when you don´t need it in order to avoid memory leaks.</p>\n"
